1552
02:04:13,885 --> 02:04:15,327
That is where we can partner.

1553
02:04:15,707 --> 02:04:25,955
And I know that there's a resolution from Councilor Scarpelli on that question and a resolution from Councilor Collins and I on that question, because that is where we can most and best engage in this discussion.

1554
02:04:26,936 --> 02:04:31,940
