02:07:36,823 --> 02:07:39,145
Point of information, if I can, Madam President.

1580
02:07:41,365 --> 02:07:43,426
the funding was there for the school system.

1581
02:07:44,446 --> 02:07:49,909
I believe it was probably 80% of the funding that was cut for security over the last four years.

1582
