02:18:34,215 --> 02:18:37,016
Let's stop, let's hold school off for the next four days, three days.

1688
02:18:37,596 --> 02:18:41,778
Let's bring our teachers into a room with our principals and let's find a solution right now.

1689
02:18:43,462 --> 02:18:45,704
So our kids are safe when it's time to go back to school.

1690
02:18:47,426 --> 02:18:49,288
Because the next few days are going to be useless.

1691
02:18:51,170 --> 02:18:52,351
There's going to be no learning.

1692
02:18:54,474 --> 02:19:00,760
I want to get solutions from groups that are going to work together to make our kids safe on January 3rd.

1693
02:19:02,001 --> 02:19:03,283
Safe when they go back to school.

1694
02:19:06,058 --> 02:19:22,129
So to protect each other because what was said in another forum and how it was presented by this counselor to people on different committees and try to protect what they're doing on the school committee side, I'm not afraid to speak for it.

1695
02:19:22,209 --> 02:19:24,011
Politically, I don't care.

1696
02:19:24,031 --> 02:19:31,016
Our kids are hurting and what people are seeing

